# Classify the message by subject — billing arm. Guarded on
# `@ticket.category == ""` so a higher-priority match (account-access at
# 100, bug-report at 110) wins. See 100/account-access.txcl for the
# EMIT + scope-ladder rationale.
WHEN @ticket.category == "" && @lmtp.msg.subject =~ /(?i)billing|invoice|refund|charge/
  EMIT @ticket.category = "billing",
       @ticket.priority = "high"
